    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>\n                  The humoral response to two doses of SARS-CoV-2 (Covid-19) vaccine among transplant recipients is inferior to immunocompetent individuals.\n                  <jats:sup>1</jats:sup>\n                  Data on the \u2018real-world\u2019 effectiveness of vaccination in kidney transplant recipients [KTRs] are lacking. We performed a cohort study to investigate the impact of vaccination on Covid-19 infection and outcomes in our kidney transplant program.\n                </jats:p>",
